snippet.title: Airport Renovator - OFFICIAL TRAILER 2
snippet.description:
Add us to your wishlist on Steam: https://store.steampowered.com/app/1356250/Airport_Renovator/

Take matters into your own hands and renovate a run-down airport! You have the right tools for the job, so clean up and restore this place. Open up the loot crates and collect pieces of equipment that you can arrange according to your plan. Make this airport an international giant!

Add us to wishlist on Steam: https://store.steampowered.com/app/1356250/Airport_Renovator/
Join our Discord: https://discord.gg/PWgnH4EaVp
Like us on Facebook: https://www.facebook.com/TwoHorizons
